      "description": "Kurv ETF Trust - Kurv Memory Select ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Kurv Investment Management LLC. It invests in public equity markets of global region. It invests directly and through derivatives in stocks of companies operating across memory chips and Information Technology sectors . It invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified market capitalization. The fund uses derivatives such as options to create its portfolio. Kurv ETF Trust - Kurv Memory Select ETF  was formed on June 30, 2026 and is domiciled in the United States.",
